    FontColor #000000
}
</style>
+ Inherited Permissions\nFrom Schema
++ Required grants
+++_ USE CATALOG on catalog
+++_ USE SCHEMA + SELECT on schema
++ Effect
+++_ SELECT on all tables in schema
+++_ Includes future tables
++ Characteristics
+++_ Less admin overhead
+++_ Less restrictive than explicit
+++_ Scoped to that schema
-- GRANT syntax
---_ GRANT SELECT ON SCHEMA ...
---_ All current + future tables
@endmindmap
